query:
INSERT INTO stop_transfer (from_stop_id, to_stop_id, transfer_type, min_transfer_time)
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::INTEGER[],
                $2::INTEGER[],
                $3::SMALLINT[],
                $4::SMALLINT[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (from_stop_id, to_stop_id) DO NOTHING
